b"I've always loved spending time in the UK and it's so gratifying to learn how this album has been embraced."
b'To have the same thing happen on "the other side of the pond" is just as exciting.'
b'When the album went to #1 in the States I was surprised and thrilled.'
b"You'd think getting news that you've been #1 in 5 consecutive decades would make you feel old, but this makes me feel young. Thank you all."
b"I was just told 'Love Is The Answer' came out at #1, and I want to share that honor with my fans, my friends, who have made that possible."
